$ Oracle Option: Real Application Testing
@ Real Application Testing


Real Application Testing allows to test system changes in a simulation of production-level workload and use.

Features:
  • SPA Quick Check
  • SQL Performance Analyzer
  • Database Replay
  • Concurrent Database Replay
  • Consolidation Workbench

With *real application testing*, it's possible to capture the workload of a 
(→ development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard#dg-standby-db[primary]) database and then reply it on a (→ development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard#dg-standby-db[standby])
DB for testing purposes.
  
sa:
 → development/databases/Oracle/Options 
